race.comment: TILLY GIRL (8) has mixed form recently, finishing fifth (25.21) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Can turn form around here. DERMOTT ROSE (5) held his own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 1.75 lengths (25.14) behind Sweet Nugget at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from eight attempts. Hard to beat again. MALLY BOY (1) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 4th (25.18) at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning six races. Worth following up. ZIPPING DARLA (2) is worth a look over a shorter trip this time.
